<<vfx_fg_fadein>>

Let's have a sample scene with two random characters.
First, we'll pick the left character.

//Number of characters.  Right now, dialogue exists only for 4.  There are 13 characters for deep dungeon so far.
<<set $leftCharRoll = dice(5)>>

//New characters are added both to THIS list AND the next one!  Don't forget!
<<if $leftCharRoll == 1>>
